title:
id: qys-dbtest-JDBC

info:
  name: qys-dbtest-JDBC
  author: thestar
  severity: critical
  description: 契约锁电子签约管理控制台dbtest接口存在JDBC反序列化漏洞可导致任意文件文件读取和远程代码执行
  reference:
  - https://le1a.github.io/article/20f7c031-1dd6-80e5-9c91-c325793a6c0e
  - https://xz.aliyun.com/news/18245
  - https://www.qiyuesuo.com/more/security/servicepack

http:
- method: GET
  path:
  - '{{RootURL}}/api/setup/dbtest'
  max-redirects: 3
  disable-cookie: true
  matchers-condition: and
  matchers:
  - type: status
    status:
    - 200
    condition: and

  - type: word
    part: body
    words:
    - code
    condition: and

  - type: word
    part: body
    words:
    - u8BF7\u586B\u5199\u4E3B\u673A\u540D\u79F0
    condition: and
